quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  73,1,"Ewe Owifimbile!"
  73,2,"Bukha mushilo shioosi, halali hatiti butswa!"
  73,3,"Eshitonye shiashio nohomba oleemiekhwo hatiti."
  73,4,"Nohomba ometekhwo, ne osoome Ikurani mushiroonyo."
  73,5,"Toto efwe khwitsa okhukwishilia likhuwa lisiro."
  73,6,"Toto okhubukha eshilo, omwoyo kukwalalanga muno, ne amakhuwa kashio kabetsanga amalunjifu muno."
  73,7,"Ne toto bwene ewe obetsanga nende okhubotokhana okhunji mushitere."
  73,8,"Kho lirumbule elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, ne irushila elala khuye."
  73,9,"Nyasaye Omulesi webukwe nende mumbo, abulaho nyasaye wundi owulali Ye tawe, khomukhole Omwisikwa wuwo."
  73,10,"Ne wifwile khukababoolanga, ne bawuyekhwo mubulayi."
  73,11,"Ne ndeshela abaingani abali mubwokholo, ne obahelesie obwiyangu butiti."
  73,12,"Toto bwene efwe khuli nende tsirimba tsisiro nende omulilo omululu."
  73,13,"Nende eshilibwa shirekamanga mumworokoro nende eshinyasio eshilulu."
  73,14,"Inyanga lwa eshialo shilirenga nende tsingulu tsiosi, ne tsingulu tsilibulungukha shinga olufu."
  73,15,"Toto efwe khwabarumila Omurumwa abe Omuloli khwinywe, shingala khwarumila Firauni omurumwa."
  73,16,"Halali Firauni naalatila amalako ka Omurumwa oyo tawe, mana nikhumutila okhutila khweshinyasio."
  73,17,"Ne shingala mukhayanga, muliba murie inyanga ya abana balimela tsimbutsi?"
  73,18,"Awo likulu liliatikha! Ne awo kayalachisilia kaliikholekha."
  73,19,"Toto bwene kano ni ametsulisio. Kho, owenya, atiile injila ya Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi."
  73,20,"Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yamanya mbu ewe wemanga nolaama ahambi eshilo shioosi, nohomba eshitonye shiashio nohomba mukhuwa khwashio, nende omukanda kulia kuli halala ninawe. Ne Nyasaye niye ureranga eshilo neshitere. Yamanya mbu shimunyala okhumanya okhushibala obulai tawe, mana nabaleshela tsimbi tsienu. Kho soome shiamunyalilwa mukurani. Yamanya mbu mwinywe balimwo abalwale, ne abandi basamulanga khushialo nibakhaaba khutsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye. Nabo abandi bakhupananga khunjila ya Nyasaye. Kho soome shiamunyalilwa mushio, mana mulaame iswala obulachweya, ne muhane eshihanwa, ne muhelesie Nyasaye likofi lilayi. Ne lilayi liosiliosi liamwiranjilisilia abeene, mulilinyoola ewa Nyasaye nilili lilayi khandi lia omurungo omukhongo muno. Ne sabe Nyasaye eshileshelo. Toto Nyasaye ni Omunji wokhuleshela, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
